file.name: AuthRequest.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: AuthRequest
  description: Collection to test authorization to request level
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: https://api.io
components:
  securitySchemes:
    basicAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
paths:
  /users:
    post:
      tags:
        - default
      summary: Create new User Copy
      description: Create a new user into your amazing API
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              example:
                example: field
                other:
                  data1: 'yes'
                  data2: 'no'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json: {}
    get:
      tags:
        - default
      summary: Get list of users
      description: Obtain a list of users that fullfill the conditions of the filters
      security:
        - basicAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: age
          in: query
          schema:
            type: integer
          description: Filter by age
          example: '45'
        - name: name
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
          description: Filter by name
          example: Jhon
        - name: review
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
          description: Indicate if should be reviewed or not
          example: 'true'
        - name: number
          in: query
          schema:
            type: number
          description: This is a number
          example: '23.56'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json: {}
